of the Western nations of Europe and of the and the United States and Canada offer the

14:14.600 --> 14:20.920
greatest hope and assurance for peace if we can stand together and work together all

14:20.920 --> 14:30.040
one for all and all for one militarily, economically and politically so that in 1949 the North

14:30.040 --> 14:33.960
Atlantic Treaty organization was created.

14:33.960 --> 14:40.280
