17:45.360 --> 17:50.400
recent weeks various members of the commission including real Clayton myself have been traveling

17:50.400 --> 17:56.960
to different countries in order to stimulate the creation of similar committees in the

17:56.960 --> 18:01.760
NATO countries so that in time we could organize a type of convention that was envisaged

18:01.760 --> 18:04.280
in the resolution.

18:04.280 --> 18:09.800
I think that that is progressing but it is a slow process because in the good many cases

18:09.800 --> 18:15.400
