Into further work of the commission is concerned I agree entirely with the very first words

18:29.000 --> 18:36.440
you said but perhaps the most important thing today the priority from the front of view

18:36.440 --> 18:41.920
of the free world is to make certain that the free nation for the world as represented

18:41.920 --> 18:48.600
in large measure by the United community should be operating from a military political and

18:48.600 --> 18:53.080
economic point of view in as close to the unit as it possibly yet.

